snippet.title: Stick to the Plan - [Official Trailer]
snippet.description:
Stick to the Plan is a relaxing and charming stick maneuvering puzzle game about Roberto, a dog who really loves loooooooong sticks with a plan in mind.


Add it to your wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2334280/Stick_to_the_Plan/

Follow us on  Twitter: https://twitter.com/DeadPixelTales

Contact: deadpixeltales@gmail.com



Created by Dead Pixel Tales
